msgid "There's something in there...!"
msgstr "裡面有東西...！"

msgid "Now is probably not a good time to go inside."
msgstr "現在進去可能不太好。"

msgid "Take ${item:ch1.bucket}?"
msgstr "拿走 ${item:ch1.bucket} 嗎？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Cool, a bucket."
msgstr "酷，一個桶子。"

msgid "You can do lots of things with that."
msgstr "妳可以用它來做很多事。"

msgid "Like...?"
msgstr "像是...？"

msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr "嗯~~..."

msgid "We could try removing all the water with it."
msgstr "我們可以試著用它把水都舀出來。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "You could wear it as a hat...?"
msgstr "妳可以把它當帽子戴上...？"

msgid "A broken terrarium."
msgstr "破掉的飼養箱。"

msgid "This looks like the box I was carrying the caterpillar in..."
msgstr "看起來像是我之前裝著毛毛蟲的箱子..."

msgid "Large windows."
msgstr "巨大的窗戶。"

msgid "You can vaguely see some machinery inside."
msgstr "妳可以隱約地看到裡面的機械構造。"

msgid "You can see something lurking inside."
msgstr "妳可以看到裡面有某種東西潛伏其中。"

msgid "There's a door here, but it won't open."
msgstr "那裡有扇門，但是打不開。"

msgid "This is the door to the surface."
msgstr "通往地表的門。"

msgid "...Huh? It's locked?"
msgstr "...嗯？鎖住了？"

msgid "Are we trapped after all?"
msgstr "我們被困住了嗎？"

msgid "It can't be, I just came through here... Do we need a key?"
msgstr "怎麼可能，我剛剛才從這裡進來...我們需要鑰匙嗎？"

msgid "There's no keyhole."
msgstr "沒有鑰匙孔。"

msgid "Huh... good eye."
msgstr "嗯...好眼力。"

msgid "We'll just have to do as Rune said and go deeper down."
msgstr "我們只能照著符石說的繼續往下走。"

msgid "There's a crack in the wall."
msgstr "牆壁有個裂痕。"
